                      <item xml:id="a3"><desc type="GuestText"><locus target="#iiir #iiiv #ivr" facs="003 004"/>Prayer <q>“For the Sake of the Honor and Glory and Covenant of Our Lady, Virgin Mary,” <foreign xml:lang="gez">በእንተ፡ ዕበያ፡ ወክብራ፡ ወኪዳና፡ ለእግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ ድንግል፡</foreign></q></desc></item>
