                      <item xml:id="a6"><desc type="OwnershipNote"><locus target="#7v" facs="015">f. 7v and passim</locus> mentions two secondary owners, Wäldä Sämaʿət (<foreign xml:lang="gez">ወልደ፡ ሰማዕት፡</foreign>) and Wäldä Giyorgis (<foreign xml:lang="gez">ወልደ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡</foreign>). The name of the original owner has been systematically erased</desc></item>
